event Approval(address indexed owner, address indexed spender, uint256 value)
event Minted(uint256[] nftIds, uint256[] amounts, address to)
event OwnershipTransferred(address indexed previousOwner, address indexed newOwner)
event Swapped(uint256[] nftIds, uint256[] amounts, uint256[] specificIds, address to)
event Transfer(address indexed from, address indexed to, uint256 value)
event VaultInit(uint256 indexed vaultId, address assetAddress, bool is1155, bool allowAllItems)
event VaultShutdown(address assetAddress, uint256 numItems, address recipient)
function __NFTXVault_init(string name_, string symbol_, address assetAddress_, bool is1155_, bool allowAllItems_)
function allowance(address owner, address spender) view returns (uint256)
function approve(address spender, uint256 amount) returns (bool)
function decreaseAllowance(address spender, uint256 subtractedValue) returns (bool)
function deployEligibilityStorage(uint256 moduleIndex, bytes initData) returns (address)
function depositInfo1155(uint256, uint256) view returns (uint256 qty, address depositor, uint48 timestamp)
function flashFee(address token, uint256 amount) view returns (uint256)
function flashLoan(address receiver, address token, uint256 amount, bytes data) returns (bool)
function getVTokenPremium1155(uint256 tokenId, uint256 amount) view returns (uint256 netPremium, uint256[] premiums, address[] depositors)
function getVTokenPremium721(uint256 tokenId) view returns (uint256 premium, address depositor)
function increaseAllowance(address spender, uint256 addedValue) returns (bool)
function mint(uint256[] tokenIds, uint256[] amounts, address depositor, address to) payable returns (uint256 vTokensMinted)
function onERC1155BatchReceived(address, address, uint256[], uint256[], bytes) returns (bytes4)
function onERC1155Received(address, address, uint256, uint256, bytes) returns (bytes4)
function onERC721Received(address, address, uint256, bytes) returns (bytes4)
function redeem(uint256[] idsOut, address to, uint256 wethAmount, bool forceFees) payable returns (uint256 ethFees)
function rescueTokens(uint8 tt, address token, uint256[] ids, uint256[] amounts)
function setFees(uint256 mintFee_, uint256 redeemFee_, uint256 swapFee_)
function setVaultFeatures(bool enableMint_, bool enableRedeem_, bool enableSwap_)
function swap(uint256[] idsIn, uint256[] amounts, uint256[] idsOut, address depositor, address to, bool forceFees) payable returns (uint256 ethFees)
function tokenDepositInfo(uint256) view returns (uint48 timestamp, address depositor)
function transfer(address to, uint256 amount) returns (bool)
function transferFrom(address from, address to, uint256 amount) returns (bool)
function vTokenToETH(uint256 vTokenAmount) view returns (uint256 ethAmount)
function vaultFees() view returns (uint256 mintFee, uint256 redeemFee, uint256 swapFee)
